snippet.title: The Elder Scrolls Online: Horns of the Reach – Official Trailer
snippet.description:
A new threat of man and beast plagues the Jerall Mountains. Are you ready to face the Dreadhorn Clan in the Horns of the Reach?

The Horns of the Reach DLC game pack includes Bloodroot Forge and Falkreath Hold, two brand new four-player dungeons. It’s free with an active ESO Plus membership, and is available now on PlayStation™4, Xbox One, and PC/Mac. To learn more about The Elder Scrolls Online and Horns of the Reach, visit these sites: 

Official Site: https://www.elderscrollsonline.com/
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/ElderScrollsOnline
Twitter: https://twitter.com/TESOnline
Instagram: https://instagram.com/elderscrollsonline
Google+: https://plus.google.com/+ElderScrollsOnline

ESRB Rating: MATURE with Blood and Gore, Sexual Themes, Use of Alcohol, and Violence. Online interactions not rated by the ESRB.
